OL,6,FJeremy Hunt's first Budget as
OL,7,FChancellor was focused on growing the
OL,8,Feconomy with numerous measures to
OL,9,Fpromote investment and boost the
OL,10,Fworkforce.
OL,12,FBut some of the changes announced have
OL,13,Fraised eyebrows, including the move to
OL,14,Fscrap the lifetime allowance on
OL,15,Fpensions, giving thousands of
OL,16,Fhigh-earners a tax cut.
OL,18,FThere is also likely to be significant
OL,19,Fbackbench discontent over so-called
OL,20,F"stealth taxes" in his Budget, as well
OL,21,Fas the expected rise in migration.
OL,3,CThe danger points for Jeremy Hunt as
OL,4,CBudget details and small print unravel
